title.narrative: China: Bayannaoer Water & Environment Comprehensive Management Project

description.narrative: To support Bayannaoer: (a) to better utilize water resources without compromising the water use for irrigation; and (b) to improve the water environment of Wuliangsuhai Lake by reducing water pollution entering such lake.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Para 5(e)(i) & (ii), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Maintain policies & procedures tomonitor and evaluate project and furnish semi-annual reports starting March 15, 2012 | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Para. 5(c)(i), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Furnish to the Bank and Inner Mongoliacertified/audited copies of financial statements and accounts and an opinion by auditors. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Para. 5(c)(ii), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Furnish to the Bank, commencing March 15,2012, financial projections for the water and wastewater operations. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Para. 5(g), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Continue monitoring the quality of waterextracted from the drainage canals, and the industrial and domestic wastewater discharge until the completion of design. |Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Para. 5(h)(i), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Furnish to the Bank a final inspection andacceptance report on the remedial works of the Yongming and Wangba Dams. | Due Date :30-Jun-2012

Finance Agreement :Para. 5(h)(ii), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Furnish to the Bank an Operation andMaintenance Plan and an Emergency Preparedness Plan for each of the Yongming and Wangba Dams and carry out O&M of dams. | Due Date:31-Dec-2012

Finance Agreement :Para. 5(i), Section II, Annex A to Schedule of PA | Description :Manage its water and wastewater operations toachieve the total revenue equals to sum of total operating expenses,depreciation and interest, less the accumulated profit or lossof previous year | Due Date :31-Dec-2016
